PASSENGER INFORMATION
CHECK IN:
In the interest of on-time service to all passengers,
please check in 30 minutes prior to scheduled depar-
ture time. Reservations not claimed 20 minutes prior
are subject to cancellation.
BAGGAGE:
The free allowance: One standard size & one medium
size suitcase may be checked plus one small carry-on
that must fit under your seat. Additional baggage or a
bag weighing over 50 pounds is subject to extra
charge and may be carried on a space-available basis.
TICKET REFUNDS:

must be refunded by the issuing party. Tickets pur-
chased alrectly trom us may be mallea to the cor-
porate office.

Universal Air Travel Plan (UATP).
